model.name: Slaviero2021 - E. coli anaerobic central carbon and energy metabolism_Version1

body.pre: This model describes the central carbon and energy metabolism of E. coli growing under anaerobic conditions. For complete information about the model see: 'Deciphering the physiological response of Escherichia coli under high ATP demand Simon Boecker, Giulia Slaviero, Thorben Schramm, Witold Szymanski, Ralf Steuer, Hannes Link, Steffen Klamt Mol Syst Biol. (2021) 17: e10504https://doi.org/10.15252/msb.202110504'
